Data availability

            The mountainous areas dataset is available at https://www.sciencebase.gov/catalog/item/638fbf72d34ed907bf7d3080. The spatial aridity index dataset is obtained from the Consortium for Spatial Information at https://cgiarcsi.community/data/global-aridity-and-pet-database/. The AW3D30 dataset, the MODIS-based LAI dataset, the ESA WorldCover and the TerraClimate dataset are available from the GEE platform. Source data are provided with this paper.
          Code availability

            GEE code for computing aspect asymmetry is available at https://code.earthengine.google.com/ffb30832c281e94a65ce47ba6587cb4e. All figures were produced using the freely available visualization libraries in R (such as ggplot2).
